public class ContactRetireWorkItem
extends com.guidewire.pl.persistence.code.BeanBase
implements KeyableBean, WorkItem
    ContactRetireWorkItem Queue of Contacts which should be checked to see if they can be retired. Work items are recorded as the ID value of (ClaimCenter) Contact entities. This is a system-internal entity.
